Installing mcrypt extension in php 7.2 version in linux
Please follow the steps listed in below url
https://websiteforstudents.com/install-php-7-2-mcrypt-module-on-ubuntu-18-04-lts/

then open php.ini located at
cd /etc/php/7.2/apache2/   //goes to the location
nano php.ini                //opens the php.ini file in editor/terminal

add below line in php.ini
extension=mcrypt.so

save by ctrl+x and enter

then restart apache by

sudo service apache2 restart

mcrypt has installed successfully in system


